REDUCER: a function that returns a piece of the application's state

-Can have many pieces of state therefore many pieces of REDUCERS

//Application State - Generated by reducers
{
  books: [ {title: 'The Martian'}, {title: 'Red Sparrow'} ],
  activeBook: {title: 'JavaScript: The Good Parts'}
}

//L7: Books Reducer
//L8: ActiveBooks Reducer
